nology App Sup-Application Administration to bring down APP\r\n2. Once App is down: - APP ADMINs please assign ticket to CTC-IT-EIS-Database Services-Oracle for a FULL refresh\r\n3. Once refresh is complete: – DBAs please assign ticket to CTC-IT-EIS-Technology App Sup-Application Administration to bring APP back up','',NULL,'2025-12-17 16:35:58','2025-12-17 16:35:58'),(421,'DCCS - INC5441604','Closed','Medium',NULL,151,'Closed',3,12,'Password reset completed',NULL,NULL,'2025-12-18 16:13:39','2025-12-18 16:13:39'),(422,'Manhattan Labour Management System Vaughan EAP - INC5443325','Closed','Medium',NULL,152,'Closed',3,5,'CPU is normal, server is up and running hence closing incident',NULL,NULL,'2025-12-18 17:03:24','2025-12-18 17:03:24'),(423,'Manhattan Labour Management System Vaughan EAP - INC5443304','Closed','Medium',NULL,152,'Closed',3,5,'CPU is normal, server is up and running hence closing incident',NULL,NULL,'2025-12-18 17:03:24','2025-12-18 17:03:24'),(424,'Vocollect - Airport - INC5443469','Closed','Medium',NULL,152,'Closed',3,5,'Restarted processor 4 , now all processors are up and running fine. Hence closing the ticket.',NULL,NULL,'2025-12-18 17:03:24','2025-12-18 17:03:24'),(425,'Vocollect - Airport - INC5443796','Closed','Medium',NULL,152,'Closed',3,5,'All Processors are up and running. Hence closing the incident.',NULL,NULL,'2025-12-18 17:03:24','2025-12-18 17:03:24'),(426,'DOM - INC5443823','Closed','Medium',NULL,152,'Closed',3,5,'MarksDirty node cleanup is done',NULL,NULL,'2025-12-18 17:03:24','2025-12-18 17:03:24'),(427,'DOM - INC5443825','Closed','Medium',NULL,152,'Closed',3,5,'FGL Dirty node cleanup is done',NULL,NULL,'2025-12-18 17:03:24','2025-12-18 17:03:24'),(428,'JDA Transport Application - Non Prod - INC5445426','Closed','Medium',NULL,155,'Closed',3,12,'Password reset comleted ( for TASK1836822 we need to do DB refresh activity, post that - we were not able to login so reset of password was required. )',NULL,NULL,'2025-12-19 14:32:04','2025-1